abstract: Demographically, they seem like people who’d want to vote out Trump. Yet at least in the battleground states, many favor Republicans.
snippet: Demographically, they seem like people who’d want to vote out Trump. Yet at least in the battleground states, many favor Republicans.
lead_paragraph: It is an article of faith for the activist base of both political parties: An ideologically pure candidate can win by turning out the base and mobilizing a new coalition of voters.

headline_main: Ayanna Pressley Endorses Elizabeth Warren for President

abstract: Voters backed progressive women and people of color to usher in a City Council more diverse than any in Boston’s history.
snippet: Voters backed progressive women and people of color to usher in a City Council more diverse than any in Boston’s history.
lead_paragraph: BOSTON — When Michelle Wu first ran for Boston’s City Council, she made get-to-know-you appointments with a series of political rainmakers, and found that their questions took on a familiar pattern.

abstract: A single-payer system can lower prices by setting them. But lots of countries regulate prices and have private insurance, too.

lead_paragraph: One way Elizabeth Warren wants to control health care spending in the United States is simple in principle: Pay doctors and hospitals significantly less.

headline_main: Warren Has Her Plan. Buttigieg Suggests Another Way to Cut Health Prices.
headline_print_headline: Warren’s Plan Targets Insurers. Buttigieg Aims at Hospitals.

abstract: Joseph R. Biden Jr. escalated the war of words between the two leading Democratic candidates, painting Elizabeth Warren as unwilling to accept criticism of her plans.
snippet: Joseph R. Biden Jr. escalated the war of words between the two leading Democratic candidates, painting Elizabeth Warren as unwilling to accept criticism of her plans.
lead_paragraph: Joseph R. Biden Jr. unfurled sharply personal new lines of attack against Senator Elizabeth Warren on Tuesday, questioning her contributions to the Democratic Party and seeking to cast her as an elitist who believes people lack courage or wisdom unless they agree with her.
